bootp_profilestext:
!----------------------------------------------------------------------
!       Profile Functions
!----------------------------------------------------------------------

  ! Note that ne_opt is normalized to 1e18 meters^{-3}.
  ! n = (0.7e20/m^3) * (1 - s^5)
  NE_TYPE = 'power_series'
  NE_OPT = 70.0 0.0 0.0 0.0 0.0 -70.0

  ! TE_OPT and TI_OPT are in units of 1 eV.
  ! T  = 2 keV * (1 - s)
  TE_TYPE = 'power_series'
  TE_OPT = 2.8e3 -2.8e3
  TI_TYPE = 'power_series'
  TI_OPT = 2.8e3 -2.8e3


  vboot_tolerance = 1.0e-2
  VBOOT_MAX_ITERATIONS=8

fe_chtccontents:
# stellopt-cthc.sub
# starter submit file for CHTC jobs
 
 universe = docker
 docker_image = benjaminfaber/stellopt_wisc:regcoil_2019a
 
 log = job_$(Cluster).log
 error = job_$(Cluster)_$(Process).err
 output = job_$(Cluster)_$(Process).out
 
 executable = submit_stellopt.sh
 arguments =
 requirements = (TARGET.has_avx == True)
 
 should_transfer_files = YES
 when_to_transfer_output = ON_EXIT
 transfer_input_files = input.stell0,nescin.out
 
 
 request_cpus = 8
 request_memory = 16GB
 
 request_disk =  10GB
 
 queue 1
fe_submitcontents:
#!/bin/tcsh
#This file is called submit-script.sh
#SBATCH --partition=centos7
#SBATCH --time=24:00:00   # run time in days-hh:mm:ss
#SBATCH --ntasks=32          # default 16 if this line not specified
#SBATCH --mem-per-cpu=4gb
#SBATCH -o out.slurm-%j.%N #
#SBATCH -e err.slurm-%j.%N #
#Make sure to change the above two lines to reflect your appropriate
# file locations for standard error and output

source /p/stellopt/ANALYSIS/jschmitt/src/module_fotd_regcoil_vc7
mpirun -n 32 --mca mtl ^psm --mca btl ^openib  /p/stellopt/ANALYSIS/jschmitt/src/STELLOPT_REGCOIL/STELLOPTV2/Release/xstelloptv2 input.stell0 >& log.stellopt
stellopt_tidyup
